        [4 11 12]
        [0 -4 0]
        sage: _find_all_ternary_qf_by_level_disc(44, 22)
        []
        sage: _find_all_ternary_qf_by_level_disc(44, 33)
        Traceback (most recent call last):
        ...
        ValueError: There are no ternary forms of this level and discriminant
    """
    cdef long long a
    cdef long long b
    cdef long long c
    cdef long long r
    cdef long long s
    cdef long long t
    cdef long long m
    cdef long long g
    cdef long long u
    cdef long long v
    cdef long long g1
